name: GeoSpatialClustering--Home-and-work-location-prediction
description: The idea of this project is to analyse and cluster locations of a driver and tag them as home, work and secondary work and non work locations. This analysis will enable us to understand the driver behaviour and work patterns thereby, optimizing work hours and pointing out anomalous behaviour.
